net.neto_framework.packets

Class EncryptionResponsePacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.neto_framework.packets.EncryptionResponsePacket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Packet

    public class EncryptionResponsePacket
extends Object
implements Packet
    The encryption response packet is sent client to server and contains the shared secret encrypted with the servers public key. This packet also contains a random byte that should be returned by the server exactly.
    Author:
    BleedObsidian (Jesse Prescott)
